data.description: This remarkable property has it all!  Privacy awaits amidst this 42.84 acre property with ZERO COVENANTS that has an established living snow fence along with numerous other trees amongst the property, and a 25 KW solar system.  The 50X70 insulated outbuilding has concrete, 220 electric, water, & a wood burning stove for heat.  The horse amenities include a 17X61 lean to with stalls and runs, tack room, arena, & fully fenced pasture.  The home is exquisite from the vaulted living room and bright kitchen with granite countertops, separate dining room that is overlooked from the upstairs balcony, main floor primary with en-suite, designated office space all on the main level.  Upstairs are 2 large bedrooms and an additional bathroom while downstairs, the walk out basement has a wet bar in the game room, rec room, theater room, another bedroom, bathroom and additional laundry hookups.  There is also a 30X30 workshop off of the garage that is heated.  This truly remarkable property has everything you have ever dreamed of!
